a successful outcome, which

00:07:11.730 --> 00:07:14.080
we are going to have.

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:21.090
We have to have because we owe
that to the future generations.

00:07:21.090 --> 00:07:24.240
And also, we'll be
back in future lives.

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:26.550
And we don't want to
live in a slag heap,

00:07:26.550 --> 00:07:29.460
or have to migrate to
a different planet.

00:07:29.460 --> 00:07:33.210
And I guarantee you,
