00:07:33.210 --> 00:07:35.790
I know that many of you are
scientifically oriented.

00:07:35.790 --> 00:07:38.380
Computer science is a big
thing around here and so forth.

00:07:38.380 --> 00:07:39.230
I know that.

00:07:39.230 --> 00:07:43.140
And you may have fallen for
the modern materialist legend

00:07:43.140 --> 00:07:46.640
that you only live this
once, this one life.

00:07:46.640 --> 00:07:49.740
But that's one thing that is
at the base of materialism

00:07:49.740 --> 00:07:53.580
is a philosophical view, which
underlies modern science.

00:07:53.580 --> 00:07:57.000
But actually, it is the one
thing that has no evidence.

00:07:57.000 --> 00:07:59.820
It is nothing but a
blind faith belief

00:07:59.820 --> 00:08:01.560
