00:08:01.560 --> 00:08:04.350
And you know that right
away from your common sense.

00:08:04.350 --> 00:08:06.780
What is one thing that no
one will ever discover?

00:08:06.780 --> 00:08:09.280
No scientist will ever discover?

00:08:09.280 --> 00:08:12.030
What is one thing that we
know for sure will never

00:08:12.030 --> 00:08:13.065
be discovered?

00:08:15.465 --> 00:08:15.965
Nothing?

00:08:18.650 --> 00:08:20.370
How about nothing?

00:08:20.370 --> 00:08:22.410
Who is going to ever
discover nothing?

00:08:22.410 --> 00:08:25.980
And is anybody going to give
them a Nobel Prize for that?

00:08:25.980 --> 00:08:27.690
No way.

00:08:27.690 --> 00:08:30.420
So the idea that someone is
going to become nothing just

00:08:30.420 --> 00:08:32.350
by the wetware--

00:08:32.350 --> 00:08:35.429
what John Perry Barlow
calls meatspace.

00:08:35.429 --> 00:08:37.650
It's because the meat level--

00:08:37.650 --> 00:08:39.179
the brain, the body--

00:08:39.179 --> 00:08:40.890
will cease at some time.

00:08:40.890 --> 00:08:42.900
But the subtle energy
of consciousness,

00:08:42.900 --> 00:08:44.600
that that then suddenly
becomes nothing.

00:08:44.600 --> 00:08:46.680
It's the one thing
in the universe that

00:08:46.680 --> 00:08:50.340
doesn't have continuity like
the law of thermodynamics,

00:08:50.340 --> 00:08:52.260
the non-destruction of energy.

00:08:52.260 --> 00:08:54.510
It's the one energy that
just becomes nothing.

00:08:54.510 --> 00:08:58.680
And the idea to become nothing
when nothing is nothing.

00:08:58.680 --> 00:09:01.020
Can you do that?

00:09:01.020 --> 00:09:01.540
Right?

00:09:01.540 --> 00:09:02.810
No one can ever do that.

00:09:02.810 --> 00:09:05.520
So therefore, the
foundation of materialism,

00:09:05.520 --> 00:09:07.810
which is supposed to be
rational and evidence based,

00:09:07.810 --> 00:09:09.290
is blind faith.

00:09:09.290 --> 00:09:11.960
It can't be anything other
than blind faith cooked up

00:09:11.960 --> 00:09:16.280
by people who were scared by
preachers that if they did this

00:09:16.280 --> 00:09:21.480
and that they might end up in
hell, which is very unpleasant.

00:09:21.480 --> 00:09:25.230
It's the most unpleasant
thing you can imagine.

00:09:25.230 --> 00:09:28.160
But once the future is
open-ended, and perhaps

00:09:28.160 --> 00:09:31.080
endless, anything is possible.

00:09:31.080 --> 00:09:33.930
So then naturally,
it's a little scary.

00:09:33.930 --> 00:09:36.460
Meanwhile, those materialists
have convinced you--

00:09:36.460 --> 00:09:39.440
and we can always debate
this in the question period--

00:09:39.440 --> 00:09:43.490
that nothingness is real
and discovery and science

00:09:43.490 --> 00:09:44.900
knows that.

00:09:44.900 --> 00:09:45.470
