00:09:45.470 --> 00:09:46.970
Science went and
put some electrodes

00:09:46.970 --> 00:09:51.080
on some piece of meat,
brain, like a dead body,

00:09:51.080 --> 00:09:53.480
and they didn't find any
action going on in there.

00:09:53.480 --> 00:09:54.200
So?

00:09:54.200 --> 00:09:56.310
Nobody ever said the mind
was still in the body.

00:09:56.310 --> 00:09:57.840
The person is dead.

00:09:57.840 --> 00:10:00.610
So that's not a discovery.

00:10:00.610 --> 00:10:02.610
