00:35:03.270 --> 00:35:07.800
had a crusade forcing people
to become Buddhists by force.

00:35:07.800 --> 00:35:09.040
It never did that.

00:35:09.040 --> 00:35:09.869
They've had wars.

00:35:09.869 --> 00:35:11.160
And they've been bad Buddhists.

00:35:11.160 --> 00:35:12.720
But they never did
it for Buddhism.

00:35:12.720 --> 00:35:13.980
They just did it for--

00:35:13.980 --> 00:35:17.700
people did it not
being Buddhist,

00:35:17.700 --> 00:35:19.710
which is a difference,
which is a little bit

00:35:19.710 --> 00:35:21.210
of on the plus side.

00:35:21.210 --> 00:35:24.330
And basically, Buddhism
always moved with commerce,

00:35:24.330 --> 00:35:25.950
with merchants.

00:35:25.950 --> 00:35:27.960
Because it wasn't into
the military thing.

00:35:27.960 --> 00:35:31.380
It was into trade
and people engaging.

00:35:31.380 --> 00:35:34.590
Buddha himself was a traitor
to the military class,

00:35:34.590 --> 00:35:37.620
which he should have
been a conqueror in.

00:35:37.620 --> 00:35:39.750
And he favored the
merchant class, actually.

00:35:39.750 --> 00:35:41.600
His main supporters
were merchants

00:35:41.600 --> 00:35:44.370
because shifting the
acquisition of wealth

00:35:44.370 --> 00:35:47.040
from military conquest
to merchant trade

00:35:47.040 --> 00:35:50.100
is a huge step
forward in history.

00:35:50.100 --> 00:35:53.280
Because the great thing about
the preference for merchants

00:35:53.280 --> 00:35:55.080
is you have your customer there.

00:35:55.080 --> 00:35:56.507
You try to make a good deal.

00:35:56.507 --> 00:35:58.590
Then you come back the
next time and they bring up

00:35:58.590 --> 00:36:00.390
something else
you can trade for.

00:36:00.390 --> 00:36:03.000
And wealth is generally
being created at both ends.

00:36:03.000 --> 00:36:05.215
And then there's a little
negotiating that goes on.

00:36:05.215 --> 00:36:06.720
The problem with
the military one

00:36:06.720 --> 00:36:10.330
is you kill your customer
right away and take everything.

00:36:10.330 --> 00:36:12.590
And then, there's nothing
to trade with the next time

00:36:12.590 --> 00:36:14.010
just whatever you can do.

00:36:14.010 --> 00:36:15.450
And that's short term.

00:36:15.450 --> 00:36:20.700
It's a bit too short term, the
piratical version of commerce.

00:36:20.700 --> 00:36:22.140
So Buddha did that.

00:36:22.140 --> 00:36:24.756
And tremendous wealth arose in
Asia in those days, therefore.

00:36:24.756 --> 00:36:26.130
And that's why
the Europeans were

00:36:26.130 --> 00:36:27.830
so bent on conquering
Asia, actually,

00:36:27.830 --> 00:36:29.410
if you know the history.

00:36:29.410 --> 00:36:30.990
And that's why also
they succeeded.

00:36:30.990 --> 00:36:33.480
Chinese invented
gunpowder, but they did not

00:36:33.480 --> 00:36:36.900
use it in warfare until they
were invaded by people who did.

00:36:36.900 --> 00:36:38.100
But they invented it.

00:36:38.100 --> 00:36:39.190
They invented the compass.

00:36:39.190 --> 00:36:41.310
They had ships that
were 10 times bigger

00:36:41.310 --> 00:36:42.300
than Columbus' ships.

00:36:42.300 --> 00:36:44.670
And they went to the
New World and to Africa.

00:36:44.670 --> 00:36:46.830
And they brought
elephants and things back.

00:36:46.830 --> 00:36:49.350
And those were
trans-people actually

00:36:49.350 --> 00:36:51.930
who did that, interestingly.

00:36:51.930 --> 00:36:55.140
The ones who made those
ships were eunuchs.

00:36:55.140 --> 00:36:57.015
They were kind of
trans, but there

00:36:57.015 --> 00:36:58.140
were a large bunch of them.

00:36:58.140 --> 00:36:59.931
And they were more
creative and intelligent

00:36:59.931 --> 00:37:01.730
than the regular Mandarins.

00:37:01.730 --> 00:37:04.600
And then, their
program was scrapped.

00:37:04.600 --> 00:37:07.260
But the point is they didn't
try to settle down or expand,

00:37:07.260 --> 00:37:09.420
like the Europeans,
and commit genocide

00:37:09.420 --> 00:37:12.360
on the native people, et cetera,
or enslave the African people.

00:37:12.360 --> 00:37:15.230
They didn't do that.

00:37:15.230 --> 00:37:17.790
So therefore, the
people who were

00:37:17.790 --> 00:37:20.360
conquered in centuries
of colonialism

00:37:20.360 --> 00:37:22.070
were the more civilized people.

00:37:22.070 --> 00:37:24.090
Some day people will
write history like that.

00:37:24.090 --> 00:37:25.470
That's what I think.

00:37:25.470 --> 00:37:26.495
They don't now.

00:37:26.495 --> 00:37:28.620
They think that European
were superior because they

00:37:28.620 --> 00:37:30.300
