And this picture is the
19-year-old Dalai Lama

00:39:14.880 --> 00:39:16.170
in 1954--

00:39:16.170 --> 00:39:18.960
or rather this is the present
Dalai Lama remembering being

00:39:18.960 --> 00:39:23.040
the 19-year-old Dalai Lama,
when he was a good friend--

00:39:23.040 --> 00:39:26.330
one of his good friends
in the Chinese government

00:39:26.330 --> 00:39:28.830
elite at that time, Communist
elite, in the beginning

00:39:28.830 --> 00:39:33.430
of the Communist
PRC, was a man called

00:39:33.430 --> 00:39:39.170
Xi Zhongxun, who just happened
to be the father Xi Jinping.

00:39:39.170 --> 00:39:43.200
And Xi Jinping himself
was born in 1953.

00:39:43.200 --> 00:39:46.631
So he was one-year-old
at that time.

00:39:46.631 --> 00:39:48.630
And Xi Jinping's father
worked with Hu Yaobang--

00:39:48.630 --> 00:39:51.360
for those who know anything
about Chinese history--

00:39:51.360 --> 00:39:54.000
who is distinguished
in the Tibetan mind

00:39:54.000 --> 00:39:59.370
by having decided that
from 1951, or '50 when

00:39:59.370 --> 00:40:04.800
the first invasion began
by the Red Army, to 1980

00:40:04.800 --> 00:40:07.550
they had made a
terrible mess in Tibet,

00:40:07.550 --> 00:40:11.240
the thought reform,
class struggle,

00:40:11.240 --> 00:40:14.835
attempt to occupy, cutting all
the trees in the eastern part,

00:40:14.835 --> 00:40:15.370
and so on.

00:40:15.370 --> 00:40:16.290
Never mind.

00:40:16.290 --> 00:40:17.280
I won't go into detail.

