But they made a terrible mess.

00:40:18.529 --> 00:40:19.920
And destroying
6,000 monasteries,

00:40:19.920 --> 00:40:21.990
killing lots of people.

00:40:21.990 --> 00:40:24.720
And so, Xi Zhongxun, and Hu
Yaobang, and Jiao Xiyang,

00:40:24.720 --> 00:40:28.110
who people have more
heard of, those three

00:40:28.110 --> 00:40:29.945
were trying to
make a nice policy.

00:40:29.945 --> 00:40:32.070
And that was a period of
relaxation of four or five

00:40:32.070 --> 00:40:34.232
years in the early
'80s in Tibet when

00:40:34.232 --> 00:40:36.690
they started rebuilding those
monasteries that tourists now

00:40:36.690 --> 00:40:37.290
visit.

00:40:37.290 --> 00:40:40.200
Because otherwise they were all
flattened before the Cultural

00:40:40.200 --> 00:40:42.070
Revolution.

00:40:42.070 --> 00:40:44.700
But then more so during
the Cultural Revolution.

00:40:44.700 --> 00:40:49.290
And then, he was
busted by Deng when

00:40:49.290 --> 00:40:51.505
Deng got older and
hardened about it

00:40:51.505 --> 00:40:53.610
and decided he
had to crush them.

00:40:53.610 --> 00:40:56.430
And he didn't want to--

00:40:56.430 --> 00:41:00.030
especially he was frightened by
the Soviet Union melting down

00:41:00.030 --> 00:41:02.850
and losing because [INAUDIBLE]
in the Baltics and all this.

00:41:02.850 --> 00:41:07.440
So he said Tibet should
be like Lithuania--

00:41:07.440 --> 00:41:09.841
Estonia, not like
Latvia and Lithuania.

00:41:09.841 --> 00:41:11.340
In other words, we
should be filled-

00:41:11.340 --> 00:41:14.110
we should settle
totally colonial settle

00:41:14.110 --> 00:41:15.630
Tibet, which has
not been possible

00:41:15.630 --> 00:41:16.980
anyway because of the altitude.

00:41:16.980 --> 00:41:18.820
But he wanted to do that.

00:41:18.820 --> 00:41:21.360
And so, that's Xi
Jinping's father.

00:41:21.360 --> 00:41:25.110
And that's Xi Jinping,
one-year-old baby.

00:41:25.110 --> 00:41:27.000
And he's getting a
blessing from Dalai Lama,

00:41:27.000 --> 00:41:29.942
but not officially because
those are the early time

00:41:29.942 --> 00:41:30.900
of the Communist thing.

00:41:30.900 --> 00:41:33.510
You can't ask for a
blessing, except from Mao.

00:41:33.510 --> 00:41:36.300
That's the only guy who
can give you a blessing.

00:41:36.300 --> 00:41:38.354
But still, he's getting
a blessing, of course.

00:41:38.354 --> 00:41:40.020
And he really-- they
were great friends.

00:41:40.020 --> 00:41:42.630
And the Dalai Lama
gave him a gold watch

00:41:42.630 --> 00:41:44.670
that somebody had
given Dalai Lama.

