And I want explain
to him that we really

00:42:08.150 --> 00:42:10.730
do want to be in a union.

00:42:10.730 --> 00:42:14.960
And we really want to
be of help to China.

00:42:14.960 --> 00:42:17.330
And we want to help rekindle
the spirituality that

00:42:17.330 --> 00:42:19.220
will make you happy.

00:42:19.220 --> 00:42:22.520
And please let us do that
and stop this nonsense.

00:42:22.520 --> 00:42:25.870
Those guys who are
doing the old crush

00:42:25.870 --> 00:42:29.330
the natives type of routine.

