And then, here, when he first
gets in 2012, he authorizes--

00:42:36.050 --> 00:42:39.410
well, I don't know that
for a fact, but I assume--

00:42:39.410 --> 00:42:41.870
this lady, who is the
head of the leader--

00:42:41.870 --> 00:42:45.440
one of the deans of the
leadership school in Beijing.

00:42:45.440 --> 00:42:49.220
And her specialty is
the minorities policies.

