and he includes secular
humanism and materialism.

00:46:11.010 --> 00:46:13.920
He's much more polite than
I am about materialists.

00:46:13.920 --> 00:46:16.560
Secular humanism consider
it like a world religion.

00:46:16.560 --> 00:46:19.860
Scientism we call it
in religious studies.

00:46:19.860 --> 00:46:22.110
And so, we have Carl Sagan
and David Bohm there.

00:46:22.110 --> 00:46:24.450
We should have had Einstein,
but we couldn't remember.

00:46:24.450 --> 00:46:26.310
He's not alive now.

00:46:26.310 --> 00:46:30.280
Sagan isn't either, but
the Dalai Lama knew him.

00:46:30.280 --> 00:46:32.230
And they were all friends.

00:46:32.230 --> 00:46:34.440
And we won't have
any religious wars,

00:46:34.440 --> 00:46:36.759
like the one that people
think is happening.

00:46:36.759 --> 00:46:38.800
And actually, Buddhists
badly are doing in Burma.

00:46:38.800 --> 00:46:39.930
I'm so sorry.

00:46:39.930 --> 00:46:40.830
That's a disgrace.

00:46:40.830 --> 00:46:44.350
And we don't defend it and
rationalize it in any way.

00:46:44.350 --> 00:46:47.980
And this is Tibet as a garden
of the medicine Buddha.

00:46:47.980 --> 00:46:51.330
That blue Buddha,
he's blue because he's

00:46:51.330 --> 00:46:55.950
looking out at human sickness
and it makes him blue.

00:46:55.950 --> 00:46:57.600
And he wants to heal it all.

00:46:57.600 --> 00:47:00.090
And he has-- he's
holding a healing plant.

00:47:00.090 --> 00:47:02.670
And he knows that the
plant world has a healing--

00:47:02.670 --> 00:47:04.570
plants want to heal us.

00:47:04.570 --> 00:47:06.752
They take all our
nasty carbon dioxide

00:47:06.752 --> 00:47:08.460
and they give us back
oxygen. They really

00:47:08.460 --> 00:47:10.200
like us, the plants.

00:47:10.200 --> 00:47:11.720
They to talk to us and heal us.

00:47:11.720 --> 00:47:13.110
They're very important.

00:47:13.110 --> 00:47:16.040
And then here is
his vision of Tibet

00:47:16.040 --> 00:47:18.800
when China wakes up to the
asset that Tibet really

00:47:18.800 --> 00:47:21.020
is, the global asset
that it really is.

00:47:21.020 --> 00:47:23.300
Not just for some
uranium under the soil,

00:47:23.300 --> 00:47:26.240
not just for bottling its water
or cutting down all its trees,

00:47:26.240 --> 00:47:27.920
or making a desert
out of its steppe

00:47:27.920 --> 00:47:31.230
by grazing the wrong
kind of animals on it.

00:47:31.230 --> 00:47:34.530
Yaks will never make a desert.

00:47:34.530 --> 00:47:36.080
That's why Tibetans
with their yaks

00:47:36.080 --> 00:47:38.070
are the right people
to be out there.

00:47:38.070 --> 00:47:40.467
But they are now shut
up by the Chinese.

00:47:40.467 --> 00:47:42.050
They're not out there
with their yaks.

00:47:42.050 --> 00:47:44.680
The wrong animals are
there making a desert.

00:47:44.680 --> 00:47:47.370
A yak never bites the grass.

00:47:47.370 --> 00:47:50.600
The yak doesn't graze
in agricultural lingo,

00:47:50.600 --> 00:47:51.170
terminology.

00:47:51.170 --> 00:47:54.510
A yak browses, like a bookstore.

00:47:54.510 --> 00:47:55.449
They browse.

00:47:55.449 --> 00:47:56.990
They lick the grass
and don't disturb

00:47:56.990 --> 00:48:00.980
the root of delicate
high altitude steppe.

00:48:00.980 --> 00:48:03.350
So this is Switzerland
of Asia, in other words,

00:48:03.350 --> 00:48:08.090
China's gem of a healing park.

00:48:08.090 --> 00:48:09.590
And the top of--
roof of the world,

00:48:09.590 --> 00:48:13.130
headwaters of all the rivers of
Asia, the water tower of Asia,

00:48:13.130 --> 00:48:15.190
the great glacier of
Tibet, the third pole, all

00:48:15.190 --> 00:48:16.490
this kind of thing.

00:48:16.490 --> 00:48:18.530
And that's medicine
Buddha in the middle.

00:48:18.530 --> 00:48:22.190
And everybody's coming from
everywhere to have a vacation,

00:48:22.190 --> 00:48:25.500
and to get healthy, and to go
to a hot spring, and to have

00:48:25.500 --> 00:48:30.350
herbal medicine, and to
hang out with the yaks.

00:48:30.350 --> 00:48:31.634
It's really a nice vision.

00:48:31.634 --> 00:48:33.050
And he's inviting
everybody there.

00:48:33.050 --> 00:48:36.017
And this is-- of course,
if China was really smart

00:48:36.017 --> 00:48:37.850
and they wanted to have
some black accounts,

00:48:37.850 --> 00:48:40.520
a few of the people, they
