00:48:40.520 --> 00:48:41.960
They could start
a banking system

00:48:41.960 --> 00:48:44.122
and write some
good privacy laws.

00:48:44.122 --> 00:48:45.330
And they'd be in great shape.

00:48:45.330 --> 00:48:46.910
But anyway, never mind.

00:48:46.910 --> 00:48:47.410
That's it.

